Bangun.

958
01:27:43,640 --> 01:27:44,808
Angkat tanganmu.

959
01:28:22,596 --> 01:28:24,097
Dasar bedebah.

960
01:28:30,729 --> 01:28:32,523
<i>Kau lupa kesepakatannya?</i>

961
01:28:32,606 --> 01:28:36,068
<i>Kita sepakat membunuh semua mata-mata.</i>

962
01:28:36,151 --> 01:28:38,028
<i>Makin besar kemungkinan petinggi</i>
